Show HN: Find which sites leaked your password in a data breach
text:
I've built a simple wrapper for the Breachdirectory API. They give me access to the password hint for any leaked passwords (eg: 4535**).

Would it be helpful if I shared those password hints in an email. Maybe you'd want to replace those passwords. Only concern is spooking people when someone else puts in their email and they receive the message.
